# Mobile Platform Rules

Respect:
- Apple/Google billing expectations
- platform-native purchase flows
- mobile trust expectations

Avoid:
- web-style aggressive upsells inside mobile apps
- inconsistent billing experiences
- platform-breaking purchase patterns

